episodes.title: She Joined A Cult, Became A Stripper, Survived DV and Is Thriving - Xanthia Gregory
episodes.description:
Xanthia Gregory has a story unlike any other. 



Thrown into a cult at a young age, married at 19, survived domestic violence, became a stripper and is now a psychotherapist helping others!



So grab a cup of your chosen liquid, sit back and hear a story about an incredible journey that's lead to an incredible life.
